392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/kate_nash_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Kate-Nash">凯特·纳什 (Kate Nash)</a>为她的“Butts For Tour Buses” OnlyFans 活动进行了辩护，她认为女性“控制自己的身体”至关重要。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="714" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/kate-nash-soundtrack-of-my-life-3442318"><b>我的生活配乐：凯特·纳什</b></a></li></ul><p>本周早些时候，这位“Foundations”歌手宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-nash-launches-butts-for-tour-buses-onlyfans-campaign-the-majority-of-artists-are-struggling-to-be-able-afford-to-actually-play-shows-3814791">她已在在线订阅服务上开设了一个帐户</a>，作为为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-nash-announces-2024-2025-uk-and-european-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3768250">周四（11 月 21 日）开始的英国和欧洲巡演</a>筹集资金的一种方式。</p><p>在解释她的决定时，她说：“虽然巡演是有史以来最好的工作，但从技术上来说，目前对于 2024 年的许多艺术家来说，这可能是一个充满激情的项目。”</p><p>她接着表示，虽然票价不断上涨，但大多数巡演音乐家“都在努力负担得起实际演出的费用”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3814813" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814813" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814813" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="凯特·纳什·巴茨 4 Tour Buses 活动海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="1500" height="2384" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x636.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1271.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x1106.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x2212.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kate-Nash-Butts-4-Tour-Buses-campaing-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1697.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814813" class="wp-caption-text">凯特·纳什·巴茨 4 Tour Buses 活动海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>“旅行、住宿、食品、促销和员工的成本也上涨了，但音乐家们并没有看到演出费用的变化来帮助支付所有这些上涨的成本，”她补充道。 “所以今年圣诞节，我要求在我的新 ONLYFANS 帐户 katenyash87 上购买我的一件商品或我的屁股，以支持我支付高薪并举办高质量的演出，因为我不会牺牲任何一件事。”</p><p>现在，纳什公开为她开设 OnlyFans 频道的决定辩护，称她想回应有关这是一件“悲伤”的事情的指控。</p><p> “别因为我创办了 onlyfans 来资助我的巡演而感到‘悲伤’，”她在 Instagram 上写道。 “这非常有力量，出售我的屁股照片很有趣，性爱也很有趣。女性控制自己的身体至关重要，我们都应该支持并为之奋斗。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCwe5snoZr1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div><